snippet.title: Path of Exile 2 - Console Announcement Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Path of Exile 2 is a free-to-play Action RPG created by Grinding Gear Games. 

Path of Exile 2 on Consoles will introduce a Couch Co-op mode as well as support Cross-Play and Cross-Progression.

Early Access is available on all platforms in late 2024
